title: Upper Unit w/Balcony for 9/1, Cherry Cabinetry, Island, Garage, A/C
posting_body: ['Updated Upper Unit w/Balcony for September 1, Garage Included, Cherry Cabinetry', 'Property Address', '6026 9th St N - #3 | Oakdale, MN 55128', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do a showing after an application is approved.', ' Each adult would apply at <URL> and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Updated upper unit in 4plex available for September 1.', ' Open floor plan between kitchen, dining area and living room.', ' Kitchen has cherry cabinets, a center island and all appliances including a dishwasher and microwave.', ' The living room has a walkout to the small balcony.', " There's an a/c unit built into the wall with remote.", 'Three bedrooms with one bath.', ' Bathroom has the same cherry cabinetry as the kitchen.', " There's a laundry room in the building, and there's a single stall detached garage included in rent.", 'Rent includes water, trash, lawn and snow', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Cats are okay with a $35/month pet fee per.', ' Sorry no dogs.', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 900', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,400.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,400.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
